{"tid":2045461,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣改善幼犬咬人問題","createTime":"2020-05-31T23:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T09:59:49.000Z","uid":84286,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"8495e2a021d44ef8a6d21ba4b435dc9d2d99eff7","tid":2045461,"uid":84286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T23:30:09.000Z","msg":"隻哥基半歲，一領養返黎已經買定哂啲骨同玩具比佢咬，一開始都冇乜野，呢排開始比骨佢佢又唔咬，比玩具佢佢又唔要，一返到屋企就好熱情咁衝過黎嗲我，但係唔知係佢熱情得滯定點，係咁咬我隻手，叫佢Stop 都唔肯停，係要扮發脾氣先肯停一陣，係一陣，跟住又無限loop,呢排兩隻手都比佢咬到又紅又瘀，上網睇教用狗帶教佢，但係一落狗帶佢又嬲，跟住就唔睬人，可以點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0880035680f59ebeff234fe7fd57c376b8afcf0","tid":2045461,"uid":60434,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T23:30:58.000Z","msg":"搵衲dee教吓佢"},{"pid":"72e42a7150330360312521bc75655693102039f0","tid":2045461,"uid":58089,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T23:31:52.000Z","msg":"佢嬲都你都要企硬 唔可以就佢 惡D佢就聽話"},{"pid":"4a25b01114fd446cab98ae4b5c8e8192f2e778c2","tid":2045461,"uid":48947,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T23:32:50.000Z","msg":"嬲就唔教不如唔好養狗<br />\n你係主人定佢係主人呀大佬"},{"pid":"38e84a8ef6c4f647e09f7e73981f4ac24b0dc24b","tid":2045461,"uid":84286,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"72e42a7150330360312521bc75655693102039f0","tid":2045461,"uid":58089,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T23:31:52.000Z","msg":"佢嬲都你都要企硬 唔可以就佢 惡D佢就聽話"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T23:36:29.000Z","msg":"係企硬，不過佢係一落帶就唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係唔識教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />次次都乖一陣又打回原型，出街個陣就聽話到仆街，一返到屋企就曳到仆街"},{"pid":"e56f2f70441f83a3b3790f75a1cea5329431b12c","tid":2045461,"uid":84286,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"4a25b01114fd446cab98ae4b5c8e8192f2e778c2","tid":2045461,"uid":48947,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T23:32:50.000Z","msg":"